# Simple API for measuring request time with generating and verifying token.

Simple API in Node.js provides usage of simple opaque token, JWT, PASETO, Fernet, Branca and Macaroons.

You can choose token by setting `USING_TOKEN` constant in `handlers.js` file.

### Start API

```console
node index.js
```

### Measure

```console
node client.js
```
